				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Here's my idea for the 50+ fire pets.
<br />

<br />
HP equal to either Air or Water of equivalent levels. (Debatable which one is more appropriate. Having LESS HP than Water means it is a VERY paper tank. Having too much means it is too powerful.)
<br />
Mitigation equal to Earth (Or maybe Air of equivalent level, debatable which is more appropriate)
<br />
Damage shield equal to double its level (DS has always been its strongest point)
<br />
Spell proc every 6 seconds equal to 20 + its level (Spell has always been its other strongest point too)
<br />
Same melee damage as Water (without backstab of course)
<br />
Warrior class<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=204546" target="_blank" class="postlink">Arch Mage Xalmat Lunaire</a> (Retired EQ1 Mage)
