				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Give it the hp of the water pet, 
<br />

<br />
give it the usual innate fire pet DS (level + 2), 
<br />

<br />
leave its melee the same (but make it a warrior anyway), and 
<br />

<br />
give it a fire-based proc that does about 300% what the water pet's proc does, and at the same rate.
<br />

<br />
That should give it "near" the DPS of the water pet (the water pet's melee and BS damage will keep it on top), but allow it to do signifigant damage via non-melee, and thus retain its former uses, as well as providing "easier to use" DPS for those who are tired of positioning the water pet and can settle for 95% of the DPS instead.<br />_________________<br />Arhallia Ironborne
<br />
