				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">We may want to ask for more than just balancing the fire pet.  We have other threads about the need for a general increase in pet DPS.  I think it might be wise to make the case for fire pet usability in the context of overal pet DPS.
<br />

<br />
As stated earlier in this thread, we have two tank pets.  We would like fire pet to be upgraded so we have 2 DPS pets.   Without making my post too long, Fire and Water should be balanced so they do similar (and very good DPS, significantly better than our epic currently does against low level mobs) DPS, but one does better against mobs that are more vulnerable to melee and the other works better against mobs that are more vulnerable to spell/proc/magic effects.
<br />

<br />
Other posts in this thread have good ideas for the details.  My main suggestion is that we don't focus on the fire pet alone, but present it in the context of all our pets together.<br />_________________<br />Szazobeaen Elebinder,
