				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I think that the pet deserves a special spot in our pets. Mainly because its our main element. I'd do several things with it. First, I'd make it healable by fire nukes. Secondly, I'd give a DS similiar to what Xalmat is suggesting. Give it moderate HP, about equal to water's HP. Thirdly make it so it does huge procs, but those huge procs also cost it health. 
<br />

<br />
I Like this solution the most, because it allows a near-roleplaying aspect to the game, while adding utility to a pet that cannot be currently used. This pet, would obviously have the most DPS of our pets, but at high risk as well. The numbers, I'd let Xalmat work out, or someone else whose been keeping up with things.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
